  "markdown": "[Skip to main content](https://www.starttofinishconstructionnh.com/#main-content)\n\nStart to Finish Construction LLC\n\n# Welcome to Start to Finish Construction LLC\n\nAt Start to Finish Construction LLC, We are dedicated to transforming your vision into reality. With years of experience in the construction industry, We pride ourselves on our commitment to quality, Efficiency, and customer satisfaction. Let us guide you through every step of your construction project, Ensuring a seamless and enjoyable experience from **_start to finish._**\n\n**_Serving all of New Hampshire and southern Maine_**\n\n### **Interested in affordable housing?**\n\n[interested](https://www.starttofinishconstructionnh.com/real-estate-investing \"Real Estate Investing\")\n\n# Services\n\n![](https://primary.jwwb.nl/public/y/x/f/temp-hvjxdpuqchibjjkdzeiq/image_6487327-high.jpg?enable-io=true&enable=upscale&crop=1.0179%3A1%2Coffset-x56&width=800)\n\n### Custom Home Building\n\n![](https://primary.jwwb.nl/public/y/x/f/temp-hvjxdpuqchibjjkdzeiq/unnamed-high.jpg?enable-io=true&enable=upscale&crop=1.0179%3A1&width=800)\n\n### **Additions, Garages, ADU's**\n\n![](https://primary.jwwb.nl/public/y/x/f/temp-hvjxdpuqchibjjkdzeiq/unnamed-high-qpiujk.jpg?enable-io=true&enable=upscale&crop=1.0179%3A1&width=800)\n\n### Decks, Gazebos, and Landings\n\n## About us\n\nStart to Finish Construction LLC is a New Hampshire-based, Licensed and fully insured construction company, specializing in bringing your construction projects from concept to completion with unparalleled skill and efficiency. Our team of experts is committed to quality craftsmanship, transparent communication, and meticulous project management, ensuring each project exceeds our clients' expectations. Whether it is a custom home, Additional Dwelling Units, or any of our many services, we approach each and every project with the same dedication and excellence.\n\n[CONTACT US TODAY!!](https://www.starttofinishconstructionnh.com/contact \"Contact\")\n\n### “Start to Finish Construction LLC exceeded our expectations! They delivered high-quality work on time and within budget. The team was professional, responsive, and easy to work with. We couldn't be happier with the additional dwelling unit!!\"\n\n### - **_Smith family_**",
